---
import DocsLayout from '../../layouts/DocsLayout.astro';
---

<DocsLayout title="CLI 가이드 — ERDify Developer Center" activePage="cli"
  description="@erdify/cli — 터미널에서 ERD를 직접 제어하는 커맨드라인 도구">

  <div class="page-header">
    <h1>CLI 가이드</h1>
    <p class="page-lead"><code>@erdify/cli</code>를 설치하면 터미널에서 다이어그램 조회·수정·DDL 추출을 바로 실행할 수 있습니다. 스크립트 자동화, CI/CD 파이프라인, AI 도구 셸 명령에 최적화되어 있습니다.</p>
  </div>

  <!-- 설치 -->
  <section class="doc-section">
    <h2>설치</h2>
    <div class="code-block">
      <div class="code-meta">
        <span class="code-file">Terminal</span>
        <button class="code-copy" data-copy="install">복사</button>
      </div>
      <pre id="copy-install">{`npm install -g @erdify/cli`}</pre>
    </div>

    <h3>로그인</h3>
    <p>API 키를 config 파일에 저장합니다. 최초 1회만 실행하면 됩니다.</p>
    <div class="code-block">
      <div class="code-meta">
        <span class="code-file">Terminal</span>
        <button class="code-copy" data-copy="login">복사</button>
      </div>
      <pre id="copy-login">{`# API 키 직접 지정
erdify login --key erd_your_api_key_here

# 또는 대화형 입력
erdify login

# 현재 설정 확인
erdify whoami`}</pre>
    </div>
    <div class="info-box">
      <strong>환경변수 우선</strong>
      <p><code>ERDIFY_API_KEY</code> 환경변수가 설정되어 있으면 config 파일보다 우선 적용됩니다. CI/CD에서 유용합니다.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- 조회 커맨드 -->
  <section class="doc-section">
    <h2>조회</h2>

    <h3>목록 조회</h3>
    <div class="code-block">
      <div class="code-meta">
        <span class="code-file">Terminal</span>
        <button class="code-copy" data-copy="list">복사</button>
      </div>
      <pre id="copy-list">{`erdify list orgs                    # 조직 목록
erdify list projects <orgId>        # 프로젝트 목록
erdify list diagrams <projectId>    # 다이어그램 목록`}</pre>
    </div>

    <h3>다이어그램 상세 조회</h3>
    <div class="code-block">
      <div class="code-meta">
        <span class="code-file">Terminal</span>
        <button class="code-copy" data-copy="get">복사</button>
      </div>
      <pre id="copy-get">{`erdify get diagram <diagramId>      # 테이블·컬럼·관계 요약
erdify get ddl <diagramId>          # DDL SQL 출력`}</pre>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- 수정 커맨드 -->
  <section class="doc-section">
    <h2>수정</h2>

    <h3>테이블</h3>
    <div class="code-block">
      <div class="code-meta">
        <span class="code-file">Terminal</span>
        <button class="code-copy" data-copy="table">복사</button>
      </div>
      <pre id="copy-table">{`erdify add table <diagramId> <name>
erdify remove table <diagramId> <tableId>
# alias: erdify rm table ...`}</pre>
    </div>

    <h3>컬럼</h3>
    <div class="code-block">
      <div class="code-meta">
        <span class="code-file">Terminal</span>
        <button class="code-copy" data-copy="column">복사</button>
      </div>
      <pre id="copy-column">{`# 추가
erdify add column <diagramId> <tableId> <name> \\
  --type <type>         # SQL 타입 (필수): uuid, varchar, integer, timestamp ...
  [--pk]                # Primary Key
  [--not-null]          # NOT NULL
  [--unique]            # UNIQUE
  [--default <value>]   # 기본값

# 수정
erdify update column <diagramId> <tableId> <columnId> \\
  [--name <name>]       # 컬럼명 변경
  [--type <type>]       # 타입 변경
  [--pk true|false]     # PK 설정/해제
  [--not-null true|false]
  [--unique true|false]
  [--default null]      # 기본값 제거

# 삭제
erdify remove column <diagramId> <tableId> <columnId>`}</pre>
    </div>

    <h3>관계 (FK)</h3>
    <div class="code-block">
      <div class="code-meta">
        <span class="code-file">Terminal</span>
        <button class="code-copy" data-copy="rel">복사</button>
      </div>
      <pre id="copy-rel">{`# 추가
erdify add rel <diagramId> <srcTableId> <tgtTableId> <cardinality>
# cardinality: one-to-one | one-to-many | many-to-one

# 삭제
erdify remove rel <diagramId> <relationshipId>`}</pre>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- 실전 예시 -->
  <section class="doc-section">
    <h2>실전 예시 — 결제 테이블 추가</h2>
    <div class="code-block">
      <div class="code-meta">
        <span class="code-file">Terminal</span>
        <button class="code-copy" data-copy="example">복사</button>
      </div>
      <pre id="copy-example">{`# 1. 다이어그램 ID 확인
erdify list orgs
# my-org  (id: org_abc)
erdify list projects org_abc
# my-project  (id: proj_xyz)
erdify list diagrams proj_xyz
# main-erd  (id: diag_123, ...)

# 2. 현재 스키마 확인
erdify get diagram diag_123
# Tables (1):
#   users [tableId: tbl_users]

# 3. orders 테이블 추가
erdify add table diag_123 orders
# Table "orders" added. tableId=tbl_orders

# 4. 컬럼 추가
erdify add column diag_123 tbl_orders id --type uuid --pk --not-null
erdify add column diag_123 tbl_orders user_id --type uuid --not-null
erdify add column diag_123 tbl_orders total --type "decimal(10,2)" --not-null
erdify add column diag_123 tbl_orders created_at --type timestamp --not-null

# 5. FK 관계 설정 (orders → users)
erdify add rel diag_123 tbl_orders tbl_users many-to-one

# 6. DDL 확인
erdify get ddl diag_123`}</pre>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- MCP vs CLI -->
  <section class="doc-section">
    <h2>MCP vs CLI</h2>
    <table class="tool-table">
      <thead>
        <tr>
          <th></th>
          <th>MCP</th>
          <th>CLI</th>
        </tr>
      </thead>
      <tbody>
        <tr>
          <td>사용 방법</td>
          <td>AI 도구에서 자연어</td>
          <td>터미널 직접 실행</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td>토큰 소모</td>
          <td>높음 (프로토콜 오버헤드)</td>
          <td>없음</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td>자동화</td>
          <td>제한적</td>
          <td>스크립트 · CI/CD 가능</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td>적합한 상황</td>
          <td>AI와 대화하며 설계</td>
          <td>반복 작업 · 파이프라인</td>
        </tr>
      </tbody>
    </table>
  </section>

  <div class="page-nav">
    <a href="/docs/mcp-integration" class="page-nav-prev">← MCP 가이드</a>
    <a href="/docs/api-reference" class="page-nav-next">REST API →</a>
  </div>
</DocsLayout>

<style>
  .page-header { margin-bottom: 48px; }
  .page-header h1 { font-size: 32px; font-weight: 800; margin-bottom: 12px; }
  .page-lead { font-size: 16px; color: var(--text-sub); line-height: 1.7; }
  .page-lead code {
    font-family: monospace;
    font-size: 14px;
    background: rgba(0,0,0,0.06);
    padding: 1px 6px;
    border-radius: 4px;
    color: var(--text);
  }

  .doc-section { margin-bottom: 56px; }
  .doc-section h2 {
    font-size: 20px;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
    padding-bottom: 10px;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
  }
  .doc-section h3 {
    font-size: 15px;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin: 24px 0 12px;
    color: var(--text);
  }
  .doc-section p { font-size: 14.5px; color: var(--text-sub); line-height: 1.75; margin-bottom: 16px; }

  .info-box {
    background: #EEF4FF;
    border: 1px solid rgba(0,100,224,0.15);
    border-radius: 10px;
    padding: 16px 20px;
    margin-top: 16px;
  }
  .info-box strong { display: block; font-size: 14px; color: var(--primary); margin-bottom: 6px; }
  .info-box p { font-size: 13.5px; color: var(--text-sub); margin: 0; }
  .info-box code {
    font-family: monospace;
    font-size: 12.5px;
    background: rgba(0,100,224,0.1);
    padding: 1px 5px;
    border-radius: 4px;
    color: var(--primary);
  }

  .code-block {
    border-radius: 10px;
    overflow: hidden;
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }
  .code-meta {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
    padding: 8px 16px;
    background: #1a2733;
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.06);
  }
  .code-file { font-size: 11px; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.45); font-family: monospace; }
  .code-copy {
    font-size: 11px;
    font-weight: 600;
    padding: 3px 10px;
    border-radius: 5px;
    border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.15);
    background: transparent;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.6);
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: all 0.15s;
    font-family: sans-serif;
  }
  .code-copy:hover { background: rgba(255,255,255,0.08); color: #fff; }
  .code-copy--copied { border-color: #34d399 !important; color: #34d399 !important; }
  .code-block pre {
    margin: 0;
    padding: 20px;
    font-family: 'Fira Code', 'Cascadia Code', monospace;
    font-size: 13px;
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: #e2e8f0;
    background: #0f1923;
    overflow-x: auto;
    white-space: pre;
  }

  .tool-table {
    width: 100%;
    border-collapse: collapse;
    font-size: 13.5px;
    margin-top: 16px;
  }
  .tool-table th {
    text-align: left;
    padding: 10px 14px;
    font-size: 11px;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.06em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--text-sub);
    background: var(--surface);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
  }
  .tool-table td {
    padding: 12px 14px;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
    color: var(--text-sub);
    vertical-align: top;
    line-height: 1.5;
  }
  .tool-table tr:last-child td { border-bottom: none; }

  .page-nav {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    padding-top: 40px;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
    margin-top: 20px;
  }
  .page-nav a { font-size: 14px; font-weight: 600; color: var(--primary); }
  .page-nav a:hover { text-decoration: underline; }
</style>

<script>
  document.querySelectorAll<HTMLButtonElement>('.code-copy').forEach((btn) => {
    btn.addEventListener('click', () => {
      const key = btn.dataset.copy!;
      const code = document.getElementById(`copy-${key}`)?.textContent ?? '';
      navigator.clipboard.writeText(code).then(() => {
        btn.textContent = '✓ 복사됨';
        btn.classList.add('code-copy--copied');
        setTimeout(() => { btn.textContent = '복사'; btn.classList.remove('code-copy--copied'); }, 2000);
      });
    });
  });
</script>
